OL,5,EBIRDWATCHERS FLOCK TO WORLDWIDE WATCH  
OL,7,BBirdwatchers are invited toEstrap on   
OL,8,Etheir binocularsBand join thousands of 
OL,9,Bpeople in a celebration of birdlife.   
OL,11,BThey'll be looking for Bellbirds in    
OL,12,BBolivia, Mesites in Madagascar,        
OL,13,BTinamous in Trinidad and Parakeets in  
OL,14,BPakistan this week.                    
OL,15,B                                       
OL,16,BMore then 90 countries are taking part 
OL,17,Bin this year'sEWorld Birdwatch,        
OL,18,Baccording to the Royal Society for the 
OL,19,BProtection of Birds (RSPB).            
