OL,5,EBIRDWATCHERS FLOCK TO WORLDWIDE WATCH  
OL,7,BJulian Pettifer, president of the RSPB,
OL,8,Bsays "WithERSPB membershipBreaching one
OL,9,Emillion,Binterest in birdwatching and  
OL,10,Bconservation has never been higher.    
OL,12,B"But while celebrating the pleasures of
OL,13,Bbirdwatching, we must not lose sight of
OL,14,BtheEurgent conservation workBneeded to 
OL,15,Bprotect birds and other wildlife."     
OL,16,B                                       
OL,17,BYou can call theEWorld Birdwatch       
OL,18,EhotlineBon 01273 299 399 for           
OL,19,Binformation on events in your area.    
